 The AI Assistant ensures that the 10,000 employees who are "Out of Office" today do not grind the othe 125,000 to a halt.
We are building a Closed-Loop System where a vacation is just a vacation—not a catastrophic risk to the business. We are moving from "manual handoffs" and "project delays" to Autonomous Operations and Operational Continuity.

